ably in a related field Blockchain experience, mainly with Ethereum, is a big bonus Knowledge of software development, QA methodologies, and release process Experience with Agile scrum methodologies Experience with Agile sprint management and bug tracking solutions, such as Jira or VersionOne Ability to multitask to meet deadlines. Experience running automated tests Understanding of the architecture around web applications (web server, client/server communication, databases, proxy, etc.) Ability to execute SQL queries and to make simple changes to existing ones Experience with Linux and ability to execute commands involving directory navigation, directory listing, and program execution Strong attention to detail and work ethic APPLY NOW News & Announcements Stay connected with Spl.yt Get Notified CONTACT US | PRIVACY POLICY ASK US ANYTHING AT HELLO@SPL.YT 2019 SPL.YT CORE FOUNDATION ALL RIGHTS RESERVED"
